sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as E-Commerce App
    participant PaymentGateway as Payment Gateway
    participant Bank

    User->>App: Add item to cart
    User->>App: Proceed to checkout
    App->>PaymentGateway: Initiate payment
    PaymentGateway->>Bank: Request payment authorization
    Bank-->>PaymentGateway: Approve or decline payment
    PaymentGateway-->>App: Payment result
    App-->>User: Show order confirmation or error